Package io.sphere.sdk.extensions.commands.updateactions

Provides the possible operations which can be performed on update commands for extensions.

    Class Description
    ChangeDestination
    Updates the destination property of a Extension.
    ChangeTriggers

    Updates the key property of a Extension.
    SetTimeoutInMs
    Updates the timeoutInMs property of a Extension.
